item.title: About
item.description: Hi there My name is Andre and I’m the author of this websit. I made it to help you present your ideas easier. We all know how hard is to start something on the web, especially these days. You need to prepare a bunch of stuff, configure them and when that’s done — create the content. So, there you have it… enjoy!
